trans-unit.source: Represents an <xref:System.Int32> property (and the value of the property) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representa um <xref:System.Int32>propriedade (e o valor da propriedade) de um componente de hardware ou software de sistema impressão.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> classe para a propriedade especificada.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente o mesmo que o nome de algumas determinado <xref:System.Int32>propriedade de um objeto de sistema de impressão, incluindo as maiúsculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objeto tem de ser escrito "AveragePagesPerMinute", não "AveragePPM" ou "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref:System.Int32>propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representa.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified attribute and gives it the specified value.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> classe para o atributo especificado e concede-lhe o valor especificado.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente o mesmo que o nome de algumas determinado <xref:System.Int32>propriedade de um objeto de sistema de impressão, incluindo as maiúsculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objeto tem de ser escrito "AveragePagesPerMinute", não "AveragePPM" ou "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref:System.Int32>propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representa.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref:System.Object> the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O valor de <xref:System.Object>a propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representa.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor da propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representa.

trans-unit.source: The property cannot be set to the value that the calling code provides.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade não é possível definir o valor que fornece o código de chamada.
